<p><strong>SCP-3327 &quot;苏联掩体群&quot; by：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmorris" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2231487); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2231487&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609769961" alt="DrMorris" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2231487)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmorris" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2231487); return false;">DrMorris</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>译者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scotoma" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3929032); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3929032&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609769961" alt="Scotoma" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3929032)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scotoma" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3929032); return false;">Scotoma</a></span><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/h-storm-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4761754); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4761754&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609769961" alt="H-Storm Z" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4761754)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/h-storm-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4761754); return false;">H-Storm Z</a></span>，原文链接<a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3327" target="_blank">http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3327</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
